{"tid":1161142,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟咩係音樂感？係咪天生？","createTime":"2019-05-19T03:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T05:22:56.000Z","uid":228995,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"965555069c3757623f2f873d120c05fa1fd6fe9f","tid":1161142,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:19:32.000Z","msg":"有無學過音樂都一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己讀書時學校逼學樂器（woodwind）<br />\n不過一直玩得唔好 成日比老師話（藝術家脾氣）<br />\n唔係無花時間練<br />\n不過自己對拍子音準都無咩天分<br />\n最後只係勉強考左張7級證書 僅僅合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n知道自己無呢方面天分<br />\n有好多人可以聽到首流行曲可以講返係咩音符，然後鋼琴彈返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能呢個技能好多人都識<br />\n但自己只係停留唱返出黎個階段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實有無學術研究過呢種能力係先天定後天？<br />\n成日話音樂感，音樂感究竟係包括咩能力？"},{"pid":"8c2e8e9801db353f8e05dbc7f343d8a4d65b94f7","tid":1161142,"uid":214036,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8e048e4dc82f39a89a49d4b5efbd655600aeaf7","tid":1161142,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"就咁睇同練習有關<br />\n你點練歌？<br />\n點藝術家皮氣法？"},{"pid":"6ff6f23ec6455e04500150475e8cf9ebc202c345","tid":1161142,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1c82fa1e9c00ff340f989398060db7ca24b5ce30","tid":1161142,"uid":17794,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:51:27.000Z","msg":"如果屋企有部琴 有時間可以試下搵鍾意聽嘅歌嘅Do 音 一開始可能要5分鐘左右 練下練下就可以幾秒就搵到"},{"pid":"f6832daec4511b7217cb93410270b05a0fbab293","tid":1161142,"uid":52539,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"聽咩音符果d<br />\n天生叫絕對音準 <br />\n相對音準就係後天 <br />\n姐係要聽第一粒音再估<br />\n<br />\n拍子 聽咩調都係有得練 <br />\n可以用類似earmaster比較方便"},{"pid":"e2062002bad511a230956c33b634689f690f5c6f","tid":1161142,"uid":228995,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6ff6f23ec6455e04500150475e8cf9ebc202c345","tid":1161142,"uid":214036,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:59:15.000Z","msg":"我認啊<br />\n不過自己又無話要嚮音樂得到咩成就<br />\n識得欣賞唔同音樂已經好好<br />\n自己寧願發展其他興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c6abbbb11169014261918ef3133af30984fee2","tid":1161142,"uid":128584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:02:08.000Z","msg":"係天生，不過假如兩個人後天都付出左同樣努力，練出黎個種無可能超越天生已經識聽個種"},{"pid":"0783817b9b08d198da98414bccc1949069da9d16","tid":1161142,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8e048e4dc82f39a89a49d4b5efbd655600aeaf7","tid":1161142,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T03:44:15.000Z","msg":"就咁睇同練習有關<br />\n你點練歌？<br />\n點藝術家皮氣法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:02:47.000Z","msg":"細個都係拍子機+睇譜吹+練手指啦<br />\n<br />\n藝術家脾氣就常見個類啦<br />\n老師真係有料，寸得起<br />\n又做過大樂團成員<br />\n<br />\n我無天分學到後期自己都覺得唔好意思浪費人地時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b37fe1a9b31ccecf1627c7d2cb5b89b84d6f2a","tid":1161142,"uid":228995,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:05:10.000Z","msg":"其實我有興趣知道<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢個&ldquo;天生&ldquo;音樂感背後科學解釋<br />\n例如係咪有種DNA決定呢種&ldquo;音樂感&rdquo;？<br />\n<br />\nlm等生物學高手分享一下"},{"pid":"04d61601b5d85cd15b0c0fef643a66952c7797e0","tid":1161142,"uid":128584,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T04:05:27.000Z","msg":"題外話，呢個世界從來唔缺天才，咩藝術家脾氣只會阻住自己成長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc8dcbae5c1b8dfe8ab17bd196888327cd90596","tid":1161142,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04d61601b5d85cd1